svg.title: Clouds of the genera Altocumulus, Altostratus and Nimbostratus: Patches (often lenticular) of altocumulus translucidus, continually changing and occurring at one or more levels
svg.desc: WMO international weather symbol: Clouds of the genera Altocumulus, Altostratus and Nimbostratus: Patches (often in the form of almonds or fish) of altocumulus, the greater part of which is semi-transparent; the clouds occur at one or more levels and the elements are continually changing in appearance
